<font size=5 face="arial"><b>Mission Statements</b></font>
<p>

The University Bookstore is the Auxiliary Service unit at the University that is charged with serving the University of Idaho community by providing a comprehensive and diverse selection of products and services which directly and indirectly foster the advancement and transmission of knowledge in support of the institution's educational mission.
<p>
The Bookstore is a retail outlet that will provide excellent service.  Goods and services will be provided based upon the concept of value at a fair price.
<p>
The University of Idaho Bookstore will also serve as a focal point, enhancing the image of the University by reflecting the University's highest educational, intellectual and social standards.

