<font face="arial"><b>Book Department</b></font>
<br>
The book department at the University of Idaho is committed to providing books, information and access to resources that directly and indirectly support academic course work and life within the university community.  The book department strives to provide these resources at the best value possible consistent with the goal of remaining a self-supportive, innovative and responsive component of the bookstore and community.
<p>

<font face="arial"><b>Computer Department</b></font>
<br>
The computer department at the University of Idaho is charged with
<ul><font size=2>
<li>Providing the technology products and services required by the students, staff, faculty, departments and administration of the University of Idaho at prices consistent with the Bookstore mission and
<p>
<li>Communicating information about technology and its application at the
   University of Idaho.
</font></ul>

The computer department will strive for continual, incremental improvement while performing these functions.
<p>

