<font face="arial"><b>Supply and General Merchandise Department</b></font>
<br>
The supply department of the University of Idaho Bookstore will provide goods and services to support the faculty, students and staff in their work and studies.  The supply department will also present goods and service that represent the University to the community at-large, alumni, visitors, local residents and others.  The supply department will be responsive, innovative and creative in supplying these products.
<p>

<font face="arial"><b>Operations Department</b></font>
<br>
The operations department of the University of Idaho Bookstore will provide
the necessary support to all units of the store so that management and fiscal information are available and accessible in a timely fashion.  The operations department will also provide promotions that are positive, innovative and continuous.

